The General is the last mob to kill for the Rogue epic and in this raid we hope to accomplish getting Arista, Ztrike, Gludiin (members of Forgotten Spirits) and me our Ragebringers. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
